data.description: This is a great starter home, downsizing property or awesome investment property with huge return potential. The curb appeal and updates in paint and flooring create and atmosphere you will want to call home. A large living room will offer a great setting for the family to relax each evening. The spacious eat in kitchen will be a cool hang out this Thanksgiving. The amazing private master bedroom will be a great place to end the day with a book. The spacious additional bedrooms will give everyone there space to have sweet dreams. Don't miss the fenced back yard where the pets and and kids will play safely. Its a short distance to Hampton Cove, the lake or downtown Huntsville. Call today!!!!
